    </p>
</div>

<div class="faq-container">

    <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What is The Rock Store?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
            The Rock Store is a fan-focused platform created to bring supporters
            closer to the legacy, inspiration, and journey of Dwayne "The Rock"
            Johnson through memberships, merchandise, collectibles, and
            exclusive experiences.
        </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What benefits do memberships include?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
            Membership benefits vary by tier and may include exclusive content,
            merchandise discounts, collector rewards, VIP community access,
            luxury gift packages, and premium fan experiences.
        </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I purchase merchandise?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
            Browse the store, select your desired item, and follow the checkout
            process. Members may also receive exclusive discounts depending on
            their membership level.
        </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Are memberships billed annually?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
            Yes. Membership plans are designed as annual subscriptions to ensure
            continued access to member benefits, exclusive rewards, and community
            privileges throughout the year.
        </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How can I contact support?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
            You can reach our support team through WhatsApp, email, or the
            contact section of the website. We aim to respond to all inquiries
            as quickly as possible.
        </div>
    </details>

</div>

</div>

</section>



    
